{"tid":2507952,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點解dse考生post barcode就值得推到佢仆街，木耳自貼成份cv自爆就咁多正義撚？","createTime":"2021-04-28T11:14:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T11:20:54.000Z","uid":343520,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80fc4222ed4f743b1712b8ba7b3db6a73f02e987","tid":2507952,"uid":343520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"Dse雞只係仲臨近畢業嘅中學生，犯錯可以話係人生必經階段姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但木耳哥已經係出左社會工作幾年嘅成年人嚟，咁大個人好應該為自己行為負責啦下話？<br />\n<br />\n成撚日上網屌鳩自己公司同上司，又四圍唱女同事點溝佢，最後比公司炒同比人告都好合理吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDse雞都識潛水息事寧人啦，木耳哥竟然用分身自貼，自推post話自己靚仔，兩單嘢到底孰輕孰重？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXZg8Cn9MHAdLR3zKm7ZairkLbrP3yr9n8kJ1HbGUVeHM?filename=8nqSokb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8nqSokb.png&h=761ea156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">正義撚呢？<br />\n又雙重標準差別待遇？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa18f8fe2aee5c1ed584083c49ad0c3d14b0af4f","tid":2507952,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:15:16.000Z","msg":"班柒頭不嬲雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"4b7c3cf442abb8ae6f81b9f22f209365d56f0be3","tid":2507952,"uid":252784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"真 啲人根本雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e55a5294dd633af10073b1263363886